+---------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
+---------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Sort: u DESC NULLS FIRST, fetch=10                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |   Projection: hits.MobilePhoneModel, count(alias1) AS u                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |     Aggregate: groupBy=[[hits.MobilePhoneModel]], aggr=[[count(alias1)]]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |       Aggregate: groupBy=[[hits.MobilePhoneModel, hits.UserID AS alias1]], aggr=[[]]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |         Filter: hits.MobilePhoneModel != LargeUtf8("")                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
|               |           TableScan: hits projection=[UserID, MobilePhoneModel], partial_filters=[hits.MobilePhoneModel != LargeUtf8("")]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
| physical_plan | SortPreservingMergeExec: [u@1 DESC], fetch=10                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
|               |   SortExec: TopK(fetch=10), expr=[u@1 DESC], preserve_partitioning=[true]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
|               |     ProjectionExec: expr=[MobilePhoneModel@0 as MobilePhoneModel, count(alias1)@1 as u]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |       AggregateExec: mode=FinalPartitioned, gby=[MobilePhoneModel@0 as MobilePhoneModel], aggr=[count(alias1)]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |
|               |         CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |           RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([MobilePhoneModel@0], 16), input_partitions=16                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |             AggregateExec: mode=Partial, gby=[MobilePhoneModel@0 as MobilePhoneModel], aggr=[count(alias1)]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |               AggregateExec: mode=FinalPartitioned, gby=[MobilePhoneModel@0 as MobilePhoneModel, alias1@1 as alias1], aggr=[]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
|               |                 CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |                   RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([MobilePhoneModel@0, alias1@1], 16), input_partitions=16                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
|               |                     AggregateExec: mode=Partial, gby=[MobilePhoneModel@1 as MobilePhoneModel, UserID@0 as alias1], aggr=[]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |                       SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |                         CayenneAccelerationExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
|               |                           BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
|               |                             DataSourceExec: file_groups={16 groups: [[/data/hits/<CAYENNE_PATH>.vortex:<RANGE>], [/data/hits/<CAYENNE_PATH>.vortex:<RANGE>], [/data/hits/<CAYENNE_PATH>.vortex:<RANGE>], [/data/hits/<CAYENNE_PATH>.vortex:<RANGE>], [/data/hits/<CAYENNE_PATH>.vortex:<RANGE>, /data/hits/<CAYENNE_PATH>.vortex:<RANGE>], ...]}, projection=[UserID, MobilePhoneModel], file_type=vortex, predicate: MobilePhoneModel@1 !=  |
